{"tid":746983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅持不斷交台灣　帛琉航空宣布停飛中國","createTime":"2018-07-18T04:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T15:42:54.000Z","uid":39628,"like":519,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ee6d29b522a6d0ec483310b32e4297905938cd","tid":746983,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"堅持不斷交台灣吞阿共恐嚇　帛琉航空宣布停飛中國<br />\n<br />\n超有Guts 因為不想與台灣斷交，遭到中國施壓禁止出團，帛琉總統仍挺直腰桿，現在傳出連帛琉航空都將停飛中國航線。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據《新頭殼》報導，去年中國曾下令禁止旅行團赴帛琉與梵蒂岡，要施壓兩國與台灣斷交，但遭帛琉總統悍然拒絕。因而迄今中國到訪帛琉旅客持續銳減，今年七八月，帛琉太平洋航空與帛琉百悅飯店幾乎沒有訂單。帛琉百悅集團稍早也向國會報告，旗下的帛琉太平洋航空(Palau Pacific Airways)將停飛中國航線。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180718/1393655/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180718%2F1393655%2F&d=t%2FClPAMlwCBvXe8NzHokip4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=68de856f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180718%2F1393655%2F&h=1afd0796\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180718/1393655/</a>"},{"pid":"ebddd76b2967e454db21b22925046ead50de84a9","tid":746983,"uid":59898,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 國際陣既兄弟"},{"pid":"515d94bf6d4bb47696e994ebec3c1d4542047b12","tid":746983,"uid":59898,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ebddd76b2967e454db21b22925046ead50de84a9","tid":746983,"uid":59898,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 國際陣既兄弟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"*間"},{"pid":"a999c22e24da789ef7f86e420b7bf4e2959f3423","tid":746983,"uid":79563,"like":123,"dislike":3,"score":120,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blo