nding more in Palau.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This development highlights the importance of a tourism policy that promotes high-value tourism rather than mass tourism, which is the key attraction for tourists.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Because of this unexpected rise in numbers, <span style=\"color: red;\">it was necessary to take action to bring down the number of tourists from mainland China because our over-arching tourism policy is to focus on a diversified tourism base, which allows us to remain within the carrying capacity of our natural environment,&rdquo;</span> Remenegsau said.</blockquote><br />\n帛琉人做開遊客生意都頂班支那客唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dead8729a91c86833aad3e988e5ba97f8e7d8e","tid":746983,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709bc92f19d400e56a65b688ca42739466985af8","tid":746983,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4bbaf1368251b8da895c7a762034b726c486008","tid":746983,"uid":192517,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"一個地方冇支那人係賣點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"香港點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de190b1c2b63f2b2c3b23302723e99b4914b4fc","tid":746983,"uid":52056,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2eb4ee672743ae731ecf125870e932eb2a750271","tid":746983,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"有咩玩，冇興趣喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pacificnote.com/single-post/2018/04/19/Palau-to-do-away-with-mass-tourism-identifies-new-target-mar